We believe that the best way to understand a culture is to sit at its table. 🥘✨

Today, we invite you to our table. "One Table, Two Cultures" has officially launched! This project by Alsancak and Wodiyamado Rotaract Clubs is a tribute to the flavors that unite us across borders.

Grab your copy today and start your culinary journey from Türkiye to Ethiopia! 📖

